    <note type="biography">
        <p>Philosopher and historian. Professor of law and general politics at the East India Company College, Haileybury, 1818–24. Married Catherine Allen, his second wife, sister-in-law of Josiah Wedgwood, in 1798. Became James Mackintosh of Kyllachy on the death of his father in 1788. Knighted, 1803. FRS, 1813.</p></note>
